  "description": "<p>昨天小米在微博上发言称：“现在是手机当电脑用，电脑当电视机用，电视机当摆设用！！！！明天上午十点，美好的事情即将发生，敬请期待……”，这一发言引发了网友的无数猜测，其中一部分网友认为这是小米在为47英寸电视造势，而另一部分用户则认为这是在为红米手机造势。<strong>今天上午十点，正当大家满怀希望的坐等小米揭晓答案的时候：</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e03e03a/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243005.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E2%80%9C%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85%E2%80%9D%E8%B0%9C%E5%BA%95%E6%8F%AD%E6%99%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243005.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E2%80%9C%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85%E2%80%9D%E8%B0%9C%E5%BA%95%E6%8F%AD%E6%99%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243005.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E2%80%9C%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85%E2%80%9D%E8%B0%9C%E5%BA%95%E6%8F%AD%E6%99%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243005.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E2%80%9C%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85%E2%80%9D%E8%B0%9C%E5%BA%95%E6%8F%AD%E6%99%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243005.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E2%80%9C%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%E6%83%85%E2%80%9D%E8%B0%9C%E5%BA%95%E6%8F%AD%E6%99%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=