  "description": "<p><strong>苹果目前还未与全球最大的移动运营商中国移动结盟。不过这种局面将有所改观。何时、如何与中国移动结盟，将有助于决定这家美国科技公司不断下滑的股价能否获得提振。</strong>按照苹果当前大约395美元的股价计算，已经较去年9月创出的历史最高价下滑了44%。作为全球曾经市值最高的公司，苹果市值最近已被埃克森美孚所超越。排除持有的现金，苹果市值已经被竞争对手谷歌超越。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e03e039/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243006.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%BB%93%E7%9B%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98+%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243006.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%BB%93%E7%9B%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98+%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243006.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%BB%93%E7%9B%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98+%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243006.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E7%BB%93%E7%9B%9F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98+%E6%9C%89%E5%8A%A9%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%B7\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" 